Usage: shiftOrigin [-help] {-center  | -lowerLeft  | -location {x y} | -delta {x y}}

-help               # Prints out the command usage
-center             # move orign point to center point of current floorplan box
                    # (bool, optional)
-delta {x y}        # move orign point with specified distance: deltaX and
                    # deltaY (point, optional)
-location {x y}     # move orign point to specified point (point, optional)
-lowerLeft          # move orign point to lower left point of current floorplan
                    # box (bool, optional)